A Proposal: The Parrot Virtual Machine Specification and Reference
Implementation 

				  Alvis Yardley


This, rather brief, document is a proposal to solicit the Parrot Development
Team's adoption of a specification and a reference implementation of the Parrot
Virtual Machine.  ....

To start, we must acknowledge the obvious: As an approach to documenting the
Parrot Virtual Machine [hereinafter PVM], Parrot Design Documents has failed.  
